  font-family: $font-family;
  font-size: $font-xs;
  line-height: 1;
  color: $color-text-secondary;
  white-space: nowrap;
}
```

Provide a structured review with: APPROVE/REQUEST_CHANGES verdict, and any specific issues found with file:line references.

